Source: hunspell
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/postgrespro/hunspell_dicts

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell
Architecture: all
Provides:
 postgresql-hunspell,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-cs-cz,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-de-de,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-en-us,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-fr,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ne-np,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nl-nl,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nn-no,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-pt-pt,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru-aot
Breaks:
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-cs-cz,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-de-de,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-en-us,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-fr,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ne-np,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nl-nl,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nn-no,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru-aot
Replaces:
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-cs-cz,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-de-de,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-en-us,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-fr,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ne-np,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nl-nl,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-nn-no,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru,
 postgresql-PGVERSION-hunspell-ru-ru-aot
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Hunspell dictionaries for PostgreSQL
 This package contains Czech, German, English, French, Nepali, Dutch,
 Norwegian, Portuguese, and Russian Hunspell dictionaries and text search
 configurations for PostgreSQL PGVERSION.
